canonical:
  title: 東郊別業
  author: 金富軾
  language: lzh
  text: 水縠微黃風浩蕩園蔬膩碧雨淋浪有時閑步田邊踞逢着漁樵咲語長
  rtl: true
  vertical: true
lzh_formatted:
  title: 東郊別業
  author: 金富軾
  language: lzh
  text: 水縠微黃風浩蕩。園蔬膩碧雨淋浪。有時閑步田邊踞。逢着漁樵咲語長。
korean:
  title: 동교 별업
  author: 김부식
  language: kor
  text: |-
    물결은 노르스럼 바람은 일렁
    원두밭 푸성귀는 비에 젖어 짙푸르구나
    이따금 한가한 걸음 밭둑에 주저앉아
    어부랑 나뭇꾼 만나 웃고 이야기 길어라
  url: https://db.itkc.or.kr/dir/item?itemId=BT#dir/node?dataId=ITKC_BT_1365A_0220_020_0250&viewSync=OT
  footnotes:
  - key: '[주-D001] 동교 별업(東郊別業) : '
    value: 별장 전원의 뜻과 같다.
  - key: '[주-D001] 縠 : '
    value: 穀
english:
  title: My Cottage on the Eastern Outskirts
  author: Kim Bu-sik
  language: eng
  text: |-
    The water ripples pale yellow as the wind sweeps wide,
    The garden greens grow thick and lustrous in the rain.
    Sometimes I wander idly to the field's edge and sit,
    Meeting fishermen and woodcutters—we laugh and talk the day away.
  footnotes:
    - The cottage represents a rustic retreat from official life, reflecting the Korean literati's idealization of countryside simplicity.
